  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc1\u0dcf\u0d9b\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd1\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0da7 - \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0dc1\u0dcf\u0d9b\u0dcf \u0d86\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dca\u0db7 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A branch of Kotalawala University to Kurunegala - Opportunity to start foreign university branches",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that private investments in providing educational opportunities for foreign students should be encouraged. He said this while giving the budget speech.",
        "The President stated that he would give the opportunity to start branch universities in Sri Lanka and that the necessary facilities would be provided through the Board of Investment.",
        "The President also mentioned that it is proposed to start a branch of Kotalawala Defense University in Kurunegala."
      ],
